		/*==========Question7 - Find pairs with given sum =========*/


		/*==========Question8 - Merge two arrays =========*/


		/*==========Question9 - Remove duplicates from array =========*/


		/*==========Question10 - Find the missing number in an array (1 to n) =========*/

